Name: Staden under Gamlestaden
About the game: Experience the town of Nya Lödöse in the early 16th century! Meet the merchant, the gravedigger, the herbalist and the other town residents and help them in three different quests. The game is based on knowledge that has been developed through archaeological investigations in Gamlestaden, Gothenburg. Can be played both with quests and in a discovery mode with background facts. Swedish audio and text only. Estimated playtime between 30 to 60 minutes.
Developers: Carolina Ask,Projektet Staden Nya Lödöse,Alexander Cobleigh,Åsa Egnér
